      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:2:1:78:8",
      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ حَدِّ الْمُصَافَحَةِ فَقَالَ دَوْرُ نَخْلَةٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hisham Bin Salim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup>, said, ‘I asked him<sup>asws</sup> about the limit of the handshake. So he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Going round a palm tree’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "8. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Hisham ibn Salim who has said the following: “Once I asked abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) ‘How often is this handshake?’ The Imam said, ‘It is just after going around a palm tree.’” "
        ]
      }
    }
